# Syncify Assets

This directory contains branding assets for Syncify.

### Markdown Shields

Use the Syncify shield in repositories and let others know that you leverage the Syncify CLI for Shopify theme development. The badge will show the version number installed in your project.

[![Developed with Syncify CLI](https://img.shields.io/badge/_Syncify_CLI_-v0.0.1--rc.1-121212.svg?labelColor=121212&color=4DBB73&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://syncify.sh)

```md
[![Developed with Syncify CLI](https://img.shields.io/github/package-json/dependency-version/panoply/syncify?labelColor=121212&color=4DBB73&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://syncify.sh)
```
